Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,3004)}So Ra No Wo To\N\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.21,0:01:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}It happened one afternoon,\Nalmost a year after I arrived at the fort.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.60,0:02:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.62,0:02:56.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've gotten really good, Kanata!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.91,0:02:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.76,0:02:58.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.91,0:03:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lately, Rio-sempai's started\Npraising me, every once in a while!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.44,0:03:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said you joined the military to\Nlearn to play the trumpet, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.06,0:03:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.23,0:03:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.26,0:03:16.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then what's your dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.18,0:03:23.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Sound of the Sky - The Horizon of Dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.58,0:03:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.64,0:03:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yours is simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.74,0:03:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be good at the trumpet, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.51,0:03:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.78,0:03:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But when I told her that...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.46,0:03:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She said, "That's a short-term\Ngoal, not a dream."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.30,0:03:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mishio's such a little brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.53,0:03:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But like, are goals and\Ndreams different?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.76,0:03:50.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm asking because I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.52,0:03:53.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.92,0:03:53.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow. Ow. Ow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.47,0:03:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're sure you know\Nhow to achieve it,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.24,0:03:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and it's close at-hand, it's a goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.52,0:04:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's far away and hazy,\Nthen I think it's a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.98,0:04:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hazy...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.60,0:04:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK, all done.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.50,0:04:13.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Don't you have a dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.49,0:04:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have one, Kureha-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.20,0:04:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.62,0:04:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.14,0:04:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You shouldn't share your dreams\Nwith people so lightly!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.51,0:04:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have one, Noël-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.32,0:04:26.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.27,0:04:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.32,0:04:31.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been rummaging around\Nwith Rio-sempai lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.89,0:04:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does it have anything\Nto do with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.44,0:04:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's for my hobby.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.52,0:04:36.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not for my dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.77,0:04:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why won't you tell us?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.34,0:04:42.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I do, I may lose a part of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.41,0:04:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Dreams, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.57,0:04:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I think about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.47,0:04:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really have any kind\Nof far-off dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.95,0:04:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It makes me kind of sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.91,0:05:01.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have one, Rio-sempai?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.52,0:05:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.94,0:05:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's so nice...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.81,0:05:14.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, just getting better at\Nthe trumpet is a big goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.47,0:05:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to be so down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.76,0:05:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.43,0:05:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't rush into adulthood like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.69,0:05:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.91,0:05:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK, then. Dreamless girl,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.20,0:05:33.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,let's focus on your immediate goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.30,0:05:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm heading out for a while.\NWhen I get back, I want you to
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.32,0:05:43.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,have mastered that song we went over,\Nup to the third movement.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.62,0:05:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's really hard-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.24,0:05:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll play it for me when I return.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.02,0:05:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.32,0:05:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aw...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.01,0:05:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But she's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.67,0:06:01.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to take it one step at\Na time! Do what I can!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.37,0:06:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That sound...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.52,0:06:10.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Claus-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.21,0:06:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem different than usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.40,0:06:20.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got my hair cut. Maybe\Nthat's why.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.52,0:06:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I came to\Ngive this to Rio...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.90,0:06:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A special message from\Nthe Roman Emperor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.00,0:06:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen one before, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.17,0:06:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He wants proof of receipt.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.07,0:06:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't leave without a\Nsignature... Is Rio in?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.68,0:06:43.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you in a hurry?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.72,0:06:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I'd like to get\Nit as soon as I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.51,0:06:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll go find her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.89,0:06:51.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right. Claus-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.69,0:06:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have a dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.93,0:06:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. When I've worked long\Nenough to get a pension,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.59,0:07:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going back to the country\Nand owning a big farm!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.07,0:07:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A farm?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.96,0:07:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.84,0:07:06.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A big one!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.71,0:07:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then I'm going to make some\Ngood rice and eat it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.67,0:07:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.84,0:07:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When your job, for so long, is just\Nrunning things from one place to another,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.86,0:07:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you want to create something yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.32,0:07:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That helps a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.84,0:07:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.34,0:07:32.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kureha-chan is making\Nlunch in the cafeteria.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.86,0:07:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you'd like, you can\Nhave my portion.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.61,0:07:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure she'd be happy to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.70,0:07:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.16,0:07:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're getting ready\Nfor the festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.82,0:08:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you OK, Kanata-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.61,0:08:18.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yumina-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.35,0:08:22.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You scared me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.28,0:08:25.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were headed straight\Nfor that pillar...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.53,0:08:28.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just learned to drive.\NIt's still hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.85,0:08:30.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You need to stay focused\Non the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.88,0:08:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.98,0:08:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mishio-san asked you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.46,0:08:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.59,0:08:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She asked what my dream is,\Nbut I couldn't answer her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.88,0:08:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I know why she\Nasked you that-
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.97,0:08:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.16,0:08:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.76,0:09:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.93,0:09:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yumina-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.91,0:09:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.75,0:09:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yumina-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.46,0:09:10.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.86,0:09:12.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yumina-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.72,0:09:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata-san, are we gonna be OK?! Are we?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.97,0:09:17.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yumina-san! I don't think we are!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.11,0:09:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.83,0:09:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone help!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.16,0:09:32.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All Gods, we offer thanks to you\Nfor the fact that we're alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.09,0:09:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are called "ema."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.06,0:09:51.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The priest told us about them.\NIn this land, they're an old tradition.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.47,0:09:56.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You write a wish, and\Nthe Gods will hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.54,0:10:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And we all decided to do it, along with\Nthe water-throwing festival this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.94,0:10:08.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.22,0:10:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Seiya-san's.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.69,0:10:14.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To marry Kanata-neechan...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.10,0:10:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.73,0:10:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.00,0:10:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm honored...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.88,0:10:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seiya-san will be disappointed that he\Ndoesn't live up to your standards.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.34,0:10:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.35,0:10:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never even thought about marriage\Nor anything like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.34,0:10:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then Mishio-san will be relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.22,0:10:42.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.69,0:10:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She really likes Seiya-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.05,0:10:54.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think that's why she asked\Nyou about your dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.63,0:10:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cute, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.07,0:11:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.57,0:11:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone has dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.58,0:11:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's kind of nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.78,0:11:11.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to write one, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.27,0:11:16.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have a dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.23,0:11:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I serve the Gods...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.91,0:11:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if I were ever to\Nleave their service,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.00,0:11:32.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to be a tailor!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.61,0:11:35.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.66,0:11:36.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.72,0:11:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to make pretty\Nclothes, in all colors!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.66,0:11:43.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soft, fluffy dresses...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.55,0:11:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ones that make you feel wonderful\Njust by wearing them!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.08,0:11:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think you're in the right\Nprofession now...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.62,0:11:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.79,0:11:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's wonderful to have\Na dream, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.61,0:11:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.54,0:12:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wonderful dreams, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.86,0:12:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my. Kanata-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.51,0:12:08.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maria-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.04,0:12:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rio left for the glass factory.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.22,0:12:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're looking for her, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.82,0:12:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The boss said her request is ready,\Nand to deliver it to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.34,0:12:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maria-san... Why do you work\Nat the glass factory?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.79,0:12:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My dream is to make something as good\Nas the boss makes, and sell it here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.02,0:12:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.33,0:12:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not putting out the works of the\Ndaughter who left me behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.15,0:12:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's awful, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.11,0:12:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You decided to go with\Nthat dork, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.81,0:12:50.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Call me Naomi-san or "Miss."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.21,0:12:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm... Mom... Go with?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.99,0:12:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.54,0:13:00.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The boss and Naomi-san\Nused to be married.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.34,0:13:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The errors of youth...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.50,0:13:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm the fruit of their love!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.37,0:13:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Maria
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.77,0:13:11.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.35,0:13:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's the proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.36,0:13:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you split up?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.76,0:13:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a hard question\Nto answer, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.95,0:13:25.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.51,0:13:30.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess we just had\Ndifferent dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.22,0:13:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Maria
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.83,0:13:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This shop was everything to me,\Nand he had his glasswork.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.49,0:13:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Neither of us could give those up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.25,0:13:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were young... Both of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.27,0:13:52.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I was the result.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.56,0:13:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK, be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.37,0:14:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get distracted by the scenery\Nand take your eyes off the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.27,0:14:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.19,0:14:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK, take care of this\Nfor me, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.18,0:14:04.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.12,0:14:05.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A necklace.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.08,0:14:07.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the Flame Maidens.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.09,0:14:10.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's odd...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.89,0:14:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should have passed\Nher at some point.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.83,0:14:23.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata, Rio might have stopped midway\Nto think about something.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.08,0:14:25.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch the sides of the road, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.41,0:14:30.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I didn't need to say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.73,0:14:49.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, someone from the Fortress will\Nbe a Flame Maiden this year again?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.84,0:14:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems so.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.96,0:14:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.44,0:14:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You heard from Kanata and them, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.81,0:15:04.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About the Roman version of\Nthe Flame Maiden legend
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.89,0:15:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that that Aisha girl\Nwas talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.75,0:15:10.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was bothering me,\Nso I looked it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.22,0:15:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it looks like the version\Nin Rome is closer
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.85,0:15:18.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to the original version\Nof the legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.50,0:15:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The mourning festival\Nheld by the people
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.90,0:15:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who had driven them\Nto their deaths
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.60,0:15:31.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,eventually became a lovely\Nstory of self-sacrifice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.74,0:15:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.93,0:15:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The truth behind the water-throwing\Nfestival?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.04,0:15:59.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.85,0:16:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rio-sempai, I found you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.09,0:16:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.26,0:16:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.31,0:16:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.32,0:16:12.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About the Flame Maidens?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.68,0:16:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did Naomi tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.05,0:16:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.78,0:16:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.32,0:16:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been hearing about people's\Ndreams all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.77,0:16:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They all had wonderful dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.34,0:16:40.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.99,0:16:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what really happened,\Nall that time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.22,0:16:52.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if it's thanks to the Flame Maidens\Nthat the town's here,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.22,0:16:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and that everyone\Nhas their dreams,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.04,0:16:57.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then that's a wonderful thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.96,0:17:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And even if the people of the\Ntown don't know the truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.42,0:17:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,on some level, they realize it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.17,0:17:08.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So they observe the festival\Nout of thanks and as an apology.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.18,0:17:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dreams, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.16,0:17:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.32,0:17:21.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The past shapes the present.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.94,0:17:24.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And because we have the present,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.39,0:17:26.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we can dream, believing\Nin the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.23,0:17:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.40,0:17:33.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.16,0:17:36.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got something else for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.87,0:17:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.16,0:17:39.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.23,0:17:42.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Claus-san needs you to sign for it,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.72,0:17:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or he can't go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.02,0:17:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.44,0:17:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for the trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.55,0:17:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really are a princess,\Naren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.50,0:17:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A letter from the Emperor, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.39,0:17:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.01,0:17:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kanata.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.52,0:18:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world is ending.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.17,0:18:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you heard about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.90,0:18:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A little...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.36,0:18:09.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the wars don't stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.30,0:18:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rome and Helvetia may\Nbe at peace for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.47,0:18:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Galia and Frank, who share\Na border with Rome...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.04,0:18:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and Gen, the superpower\Nto the west...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.87,0:18:27.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even as we speak, most\Ncountries are fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.05,0:18:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fighting over the small bit\Nof land left to humanity,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.47,0:18:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,shaving away at what's\Nleft of the population!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.21,0:18:36.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Small bit of land?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.10,0:18:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.20,0:18:42.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've never seen one\Nbefore, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.64,0:18:44.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a world map.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.87,0:18:47.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was made in Rome.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.96,0:18:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are a lot of unexplored areas,\Nor areas where people can't go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.95,0:18:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's very speculative, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.11,0:19:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Helvetia.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.08,0:19:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so small!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.92,0:19:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But most of this big continent,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.29,0:19:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,which used to be called Eurasia,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.73,0:19:12.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is now a dead zone, No Man's Land.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.34,0:19:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.20,0:19:18.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the No Man's Land\Nkeeps expanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.24,0:19:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Out here on the borderlands\Nof Seize, it's still OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.01,0:19:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the northern part of Rome\Nis being devoured by desert.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.97,0:19:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They say it won't be long before\Nit engulfs all of Rome.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.52,0:19:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I went to Rome, prepared\Nto marry,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.00,0:19:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I saw for myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.57,0:19:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world is truly ending.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.77,0:19:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need to stop the fighting,\Nas soon as we can...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.74,0:20:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before the world ends.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.26,0:20:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that your dream, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.73,0:20:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To make a peaceful world?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.03,0:20:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.14,0:20:14.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.96,0:20:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, the way Mishio\Nput it, it's a goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.98,0:20:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what's your dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.89,0:20:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.39,0:20:34.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All set!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.07,0:20:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.23,0:20:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noël-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.22,0:20:40.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.07,0:20:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really floating...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.58,0:20:59.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.95,0:21:01.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good work, Noël-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.67,0:21:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.38,0:21:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.47,0:21:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, sempai!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.15,0:21:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Takemikazuchi\Nis so small now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.46,0:21:48.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The town!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.49,0:21:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first step to my dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.03,0:21:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was young, my\Nmom told me this:
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.30,0:22:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the ends of the Earth,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.55,0:22:06.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there's a reborn sea that's\Nbirthing new life.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.41,0:22:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to search for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.92,0:22:12.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This balloon's the first step.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.76,0:22:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next, I'm going to bring\Nback airplanes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.20,0:22:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Machines that let people fly,\Nlike birds, through the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.89,0:22:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, I'm going to the ends\Nof the Earth and beyond!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.43,0:22:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beyond the ends of the Earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.77,0:22:36.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's still a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.79,0:22:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's still far-off.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.51,0:22:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But someday, I'll make it\Nmore than just a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.24,0:22:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make it reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.66,0:23:02.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK. Let's decide this year's\NFlame Maiden.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.86,0:23:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No drawing lots this year!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.90,0:23:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.70,0:23:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'Cause last year...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.05,0:23:11.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.07,0:23:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's do it by rock-paper-scissors.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.25,0:23:16.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One round.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.00,0:23:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me introduce you to...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.13,0:23:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks great, Kana-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.01,0:23:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.17,0:23:39.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK, let's finish you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.28,0:23:58.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been exactly one year\Nsince you came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.91,0:24:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gone by fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.34,0:24:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rio-sempai. I've decided\Non my dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.08,0:24:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I follow you, always?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.39,0:24:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to share your dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.65,0:24:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.02,0:24:28.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.51,0:24:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She'll follow my dream, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.36,0:24:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.36,0:24:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wrote one of these.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.82,0:24:43.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.58,0:24:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.36,0:24:52.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be a military doctor\Nand save lots of lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.86,0:24:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Once, my dream\Nwas my sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.98,0:25:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But now...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.48,0:25:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.98,0:25:05.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My mom was a medic,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.71,0:25:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but when Aisha was shot...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.27,0:25:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm her daughter, but I\Ncouldn't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.30,0:25:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hated it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.90,0:25:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you'll be able to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.57,0:25:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.16,0:25:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A pretty bride...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.68,0:25:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.90,0:25:39.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you'll be a\Nwonderful bride!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.67,0:25:43.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure there's a really strange guy\Nout there, and you're just his type!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.72,0:25:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.19,0:25:46.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.32,0:25:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm going to follow\Nmy own dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.05,0:25:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you write?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.31,0:25:58.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wrote that I wanted to be\Nwith everyone forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.56,0:26:00.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How normal...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.92,0:26:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's awful!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.13,0:26:08.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So someday, you'll find your\Ndream and start to follow it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.81,0:26:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Your dream...\NAnd yours alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.39,0:26:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Until then, I'll take your\Nhand and lead you...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.14,0:26:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Until you find your own dream,\Nyour own sound,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.12,0:26:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and begin to play it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.00,0:26:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can hear the footsteps of dreams\Nand the voices of the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.83,0:26:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.62,0:26:41.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll always be here. So\Nwherever you are,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.67,0:26:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you have a place to return to.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.48,0:26:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Filicia...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.32,0:26:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rio-sempai! Rio-sempai!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.12,0:26:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's go where\Nour dreams lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.61,0:27:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if the world\Nends someday...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.00,0:27:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Our future will go on,\Nright until that fateful moment.
